					<p>I'm a developer with a journalist's brain, a designer's eye, and a builder's heart. Over the last decade, I've moved fluidly between storytelling, strategy, and software—whether that meant pioneering interactive infographics in a legacy newsroom, launching enterprise-grade WordPress builds, or obsessing over accessibility and user empathy. The through-line? Relentless curiosity and self-directed mastery.</p>

