					<p>These days, I'm the COO and UI lead at <a href="https://thekestrel.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Kestrel Co.</a>, a boutique dev agency where I help shape both the work and the workflows. I’m known for wearing many hats—sometimes in the same meeting. Design audits, accessibility reviews, CSS bug hunts, pricing strategy, proposals, GTM tracking setups—I’ve done them all. And I believe my superpower is making teams feel calm, collaborative, and inspired.</p>

